Meanwhile, Giovanni's son has taken over for him, and a scientist makes a few discoveries -WHY DO I FIND THE WEIRDEST THINGS?! I decided to go see what had happened in my home fandom... Here we go. She was rich, beautiful, and talented. She was a MarySue by definition. But what happens when that perfect world crashes...and she ends up in ancient Egypt. -She's STILL a MarySue. Mokuba's getting married, Seto's miserable, and there's a bride on the loose. -They grow up so fa- SUE! Pegasus loves Siegfried and wants to win him back, but can he convince him he's not just trying to get in his bed? How can he convince Siegfried that love is worth the risk of getting hurt again? -Possible pairing but the combo makes my skin crawl. Malik's cousin moves in. She also has an Item and yami. But, when a wish is made, all the lights are turned into chibi's! -oh yay. /sarcasm t's been a year since returning the YuGiOh guys to their own world. Here comes a new summer...and new adventures! A new Seto Kaiba fanfic in which I am telling the story from Pegasus's daughter's point of veiw.In this story Jasmine Pegasus will realize weaknesses, overcome fears, and learn to open her heart up to people. -And speak of love, friendship and PONIES! :D Mai wants to be the best. Mokuba wants to be loved. These goals, as unrelated as they seem, draw them together, rather unexpectedly. Can a ridiculous, unrealistic crush transform into love? And should it? -NO! IT SHOULDN'T! IT SHOULDN'T!!!!!! --- Let's try another one of my fandoms. What must a body do for good Jezebel/Cain?? --- When Kirsten becomes the Priestess of Shiho, she has to find her FIVE celestial warriors, summon the GODDESS, defeat the new villians who are really the evil celestial warriors, and defeat her rival from her world sounds easy, right? -Of course not! Toki and her Po'ed 'Oneesan' Nahoko get sucked into tUotFG as the 'sacrificial stars' and find the true meaning of friendship, love, betrayal, and most of all, sacrifice. NOT A MARYSUE! -Mention of Toki, I laughed. tUotFG, I laughed. NOT A MARYSUE!, I laughed so hard, I died. Miaka finds some old letters... -And burns them to roast marshmallows. A young boy and his fellow seishis will do anything to protect their Merlion No Miko! -Hey guys... as far as I'm concerned.. THERE WAS NO MERLION! Miahome used to have another Name, what could it possibly be? Trapped in Seiryus clutches, a Celestial Warrior triggers her memory, breaking free... -Mia...home?? One final Summoner, One final God, one final chapter to the story of Fushigi Yuugi. Up until now, the fifth God, Tenkyoku, was never summoned. Now however, with the arrival of a girl and her brother, that chance may just happen. Only why is it a Priest? -BECAUSE THIS IS A TWITCHFIC! My OC version of Fushigi Yuugi. What does OC mean? Well anyway, good night....zzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz -No words... no words can express my shock... basically a song fic to rascall flatts what hurts the most on the things houki regrets that she never shared with Hotohori -Wha?? o.o Miaka Yuki, better known as Suzaku, the greatest assassin known to Tokyo, is presented with her greatest challenge yet, to murder the man named Tamahome. What happens when the job becomes a little too personal and her heart overtakes her will to kill? -AUs make my head go ow. --------- Lesson learned: Never pop in there again. There were so many sues, I didn't know where to start. X.x Let's try something tame... Like Harvest Moon. --------- Nikki is a goth in Mineral Town, and with the help of the voices in her head, she goes on a KILLING SPREE! -...so much for sane.

pointed me in the way of this fic. It makes me hurl. Title of The abomination of nature Fanfic: Never Okay (Yeah. Kahran will NOT be OKAY after reading this. Kahran will have to go get her stomach pumped. Kahran is gonna puke.) Name of The culprit Author: The Original Kitsune Ryu (Yeah, coz, foxes and dragons don't mate.) Creative summary: Mokuba is having problems, so he does something that hurts Seto more than him. But why? SetoxMokuba incest, as of now. Cause I decided to continue. If such content offends you, please, don't bother to email and call me sick, it won't work. (Yeah, so, instead of emailing you, I'll spork you here.) "Mokuba, we know that you've been cutting yourself. A young man came to me today, telling me that he saw cuts all over your arms and legs. You aren't in trouble, let me tell you that right now. We want to help you, in anyway we can. You have people here for you, you don't have to go through this time of your life by yourself. I know that you have your brother, and your friends, that sweet young Vanessa. Before we go on, is there anything else you would like to say?" Yeah. Who the fuck's Vanessa?" He climbs out of the car, stumbling on his long pants before quickly walking into the house. After the door closes behind him, I slump against the car, burying my head in my hands. I just want to double over in pain, sob my eyes out for what I did to him, ignoring him, working too much. I feel like God decided to punish him for my sins, instead of punishing me outright, he decided to hurt the person most precious to me so I would feel like this. He's punishing me for feeling for Mokuba like I do, telling me that it's wrong. Wrong.. wrong to be in a fic like this. Wrong to be written so OOCly. Why? Why don't I just cut myself too? Maybe I'll end up liking it? No! This is wrong! God hates me! I believe in him now! I'm going to hell!! "... Okay, hunny, baby, just stay right there and I'll be there in no more than ten minutes, okay?" "A-alright." "See you in a couple of minutes, darling. Buh bye." "Bye." She hangs up, and I know she's going to packing up every sweet thing in her house to bring here, to curl up around me and tell me that I'm wonderful and she loves me. I love her too, and the fact that I have her to be there when I need her makes the tears in my eyes escape. She a wonderful friend, and like a big sister when my brother... decided that he was Christian and converted, leaving me alone to wangst about my soul going to hell because I was a cutter!!!! --- The man raises an eyebrow. Well, fuck you too. Get me a thermometer, damnit! "I'm Seto Kaiba, Mokuba's brother. Explain to me why I shouldn't throw you out on your arse?" Seto's rude at times... but not THAT rude... His lips feel like satin, or silk, or that crazy mixture of velvet satin silk they use in those stupid new age kimono. It doesn't matter. My lips are pressed against his and it's nirvana. I want to taste him, so I push his yeilding lips open with my tongue and delve into his mouth. I let out a small sound of appretiation at the warmth and taste of the delicious cavern of his mouth. It's appreciation. Mokuba squeals in delight, literally attacking his poor treat. I watch him bring the spoon to his lips and hear the click of metal on metal. I frown and stare intently at my brother's mouth, catching a glimpse of a dark metal stud. I almost say 'Oh shit!' aloud. Oh shit! I frown and let out a small laugh. I would normally be extremely ecstatic if my one and only love said I was 'pretty', but Seto's my big brother, and he's supposed to say stuff like that. I take another bite of my sorbet and mutter, "Don't forget the fact that I'm a fag." Now get over here and give your aniki a hug. ----- MAN that was fun!

So, Sami Otaku, see the genious that was made by your masterpiece! -Genious? /:) Ryou's young and his mother and sister died. He gets the ring and Bakura appears. What is the spirit to do?
